Package: SocialCampaignRankR
Title: Ranking Social Media Channels Using Fuzzy MCDA Methods
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Damian", "Adamczyk", email = "damian.adamczyk@student.edu.pl", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    Tools for ranking social media channels or marketing campaigns using
    multi-criteria decision analysis (MCDA). The package supports fuzzy data
    representation with triangular fuzzy numbers (TFN), weighting of criteria
    using the Best-Worst Method (BWM), and ranking alternatives with Fuzzy
    TOPSIS, Fuzzy VIKOR, and Fuzzy WASPAS methods. A meta-ranking based on
    RankAggreg is also provided.
